<section class="l-home-splash">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="row margin-md">
			<div class="row margin-xs">
				<div class="col-xs-12">
					<% link_to 'material-handling.html' do %>
						<h3 class="u-text-center">Material Handling</h3>
					<% end %>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-2 col-md-3">
				<div class="m-point">
					<%= image_tag 'polycord-2.jpg' %>
					<h4>Polycords</h4>
					<p>
						Polycord is commonly referred to as poly cord, urethane cord or polyurethane cord. It is the standard material in producing polyurethane belts/ polyurethane orings. It comes on rolls and we sell it by the foot. 
					</p>
					<%= link_to 'Learn More', 'polycord.html', :class=>'u-btn trans-black' %>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-2 col-md-3">
				<div class="m-point">
					<%= image_tag 'polyurethane-sq.jpg' %>
					<h4>Polyurethane Belts</h4>
					<p>
						These are used in numerous applications.  The most common application is in material handling equipment. These are lineshaft conveyors, roller to roller conveyors, pop up diverters, and transfer systems.
					</p>
					<%= link_to 'Learn More', 'polyurethane-belts.html', :class=>'u-btn trans-black' %>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-2 col-md-3">
				<div class="m-point">
					<%= image_tag 'twisted-5.jpg' %>
					<h4>Twisted O-Rings</h4>
					<p>
						Twisted o-rings are an excellent alternative to polyurethane belts for lineshaft conveyors, roller to roller conveyors, or transfer belts in the material handling industry.
					</p>
					<%= link_to 'Learn More', 'twisted-o-rings.html', :class=>'u-btn trans-black' %>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-2 col-md-3">
				<div class="m-point">
					<%= image_tag 'spools-2.jpg' %>
					<h4>Spools</h4>
					<p>
						We stock both Regular Spools and Split Spools for your Line Shaft Conveyors. Our Regular Spools are tough and manufactured to keep up with the daily operations of a large Distribution Center.
					</p>
					<%= link_to 'Learn More', 'spools.html', :class=>'u-btn trans-black' %>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<section class="l-home-message">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="row margin-lg">
			<div class="col-xs-12">
				<h3>Superior Quality</h3>
				<p>
					In our facility we focus on quality not quantity. We operate under classic simple principles of quality and creating our products the right way every time. We manufacture our own yarn ensuring the quality of the product used in our belts and bands.
				</p>
				<h4>We use American made materials with American Labor.</h4>
				<p>
					We are a simple company out of South Carolina with strong roots in the textile industry. At each phase of production, we have quality control in place. Since all our belts are made from the ground up in our facility; we know that the belt that puts your production floor to work was created with superior quality. 
				</p>
				<%= link_to 'About Us', 'about.html', :class=>'u-btn u-btn-lg trans-white' %>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

